overview: Missy requests your presence for an intimate evening of stimulating conversation, laughter, and provocative revelations. With no questions off limits, Missy promises to go all the way. But you must be able to handle her!  She’s getting ready for you…She’s slipping into something special…A spritz of perfume… Adjusting the bra straps…Come on in.
title: YouShoot: Missy Hyatt
